             United in diversity : Anthems and Flags of the E.U.

    Notre Europe, Jacques Delors Institute nous propose cette excellente
   étude des hymnes et drapeaux de l'Union européenne.


   This study's purpose is to highlight the meanings and context
   underlying the appearance of the main symbols attached to each EU
   member country, that are the national anthem and the flag, by also
   associating the portrayal of this union.

